Homepage: https://github.com/electron/asar

Package: asar
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, nodejs (>= 22)
Description: Electron archive format tool
 asar is the official command-line tool for creating and extracting .asar
 archives — the format used by Electron applications to bundle their source
 files. Supports pack, extract, list, and extract-file operations.
 .
 This package vendors @electron/asar 4.2.0 and its JavaScript dependencies.
 Node.js 22 or later is required at runtime (provided by the nodejs package
 in Ubuntu 26.04 universe).
